# Car API

## Testing with Postman

### GET all cars
- Method: GET
- URL: http://localhost:8080/api

### POST a new car
- Method: POST
- URL: http://localhost:8080/api
- Body: JSON format with keys `make`, `model`, `seats` (e.g., `{"make": "Toyota", "model": "Camry", "seats": 4}`)

### DELETE a car by ID
- Method: DELETE
- URL: http://localhost:8080/api/{id}
  - Replace `{id}` with the ID of the car you want to delete

### PUT update a car by ID
- Method: PUT
- URL: http://localhost:8080/api/{id}
  - Replace `{id}` with the ID of the car you want to update
- Body: JSON format with keys `make`, `model`, `seats` (e.g., `{"model": "Corolla", "seats": 5}`)
